<% layout('layouts/main') -%>
<section class="container py-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
        <div class="card-body p-4 p-lg-5">
          <h1 class="h2 fw-semibold text-dark mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-secondary">Last updated: July 5, 2026</p>
          <hr class="my-4">
          <p class="text-secondary">At ToolNest, we prioritize your privacy and data security. Below is a detailed overview of how we handle information:</p>
          
          <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-dark mt-4 mb-3">1. Anonymous Workspaces</h2>
          <p class="text-secondary">We do not require account registration. When you access ToolNest, we generate a temporary workspace session linked to a secure cryptographic token stored in a signed cookie. We do not link this session to your IP address or personal identity.</p>
          
          <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-dark mt-4 mb-3">2. File Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-secondary">Any files uploaded or processed through ToolNest are stored temporarily in isolated system directories. All uploaded files, processed files, and session metadata are strictly deleted after 10 minutes of inactivity via our automated database TTL and cleanup scheduler.</p>
          
          <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold text-dark mt-4 mb-3">3. Security Audits and Tracking</h2>
          <p class="text-secondary">We monitor high-severity security events (such as rate-limiting triggers or input anomalies) using database logging to prevent denial of service (DoS) and abuse. IP addresses are hashed immediately to guarantee anonymity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
